snippet.title: Arcade Game: 005 (1981 Sega)
snippet.description:
A maze type shooting game where you play secret agent 005, your mission is to take a briefcase filled with secret documents to a waiting helicopter. But, enemy agents are everywhere, trying to thwart your every move, luckily you are armed with cannisters of gas.

Note: This game has 5 levels. Aftter the 5th level, the game restarts at level 1. I cheated when the game restarts at level 1 after the 5th level.
